Function# vmnet_network_configuration_set_mtu(_:_:)

Mac Catalyst 13.0+macOS 26.0+

```
func vmnet_network_configuration_set_mtu(
    _ config: vmnet_network_configuration_ref,
    _ mtu: UInt32
) -> vmnet_return_t
```

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_mtu(_:_:)#parameters)

`config`The network configuration object to be modified.

`mtu`The MTU.

## [Return Value](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_mtu(_:_:)#return-value)

VMNET_SUCCESS on success, error otherwise.

## [Discussion](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_mtu(_:_:)#discussion)

Configures the maximum transmission unit (MTU) for a vmnet network.
